      "description": "Presented is a masterclass in grand touring engineering: a pristine A80 chassis powered by the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged 3.0L inline-six. This specimen features the reinforced Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power through a factory helical limited-slip differential. The forced induction system operates via its original sequential ceramic-wheel turbos, providing linear boost across the rev range. Every component, from the magnesium valve covers to the double-wishbone suspension, remains in factory-correct condition. With an unblemished undercarriage and zero modifications to the fuel map or boost controller, this vehicle offers the precise mechanical feedback and structural integrity expected of a collector-grade survivor.",
